					<p>Thank you, I&#8217;m glad it worked for you!</p>
<p>I am very glad the temporal paradox did become apparent, although I still think it needs more honed writing.</p>
<p>The discomfort on the first reading sits well with me. I have a strong fascination with short stories that make you go &#8220;Oh, that&#8217;s what that was!&#8221; at the end, and force a re-read. These are my secret pleasures, but I hope they don&#8217;t get too irritating!</p>
